  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA76">
<l>vicumpil vitiyuṭaiya viṇṇōr paṇintu</l>
<l>pacumpoṉ maṇimakuṭan tēyppa - mucinteṅku</l>
<l>mentāy taḻumpēṟi yēpāvam pollāvā</l>
<l>mantā maraipō laṭi</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Since the celestials possessing the rule of heaven humble themselves</l>
<l>and diminish [their] crowns with green gold [and] jewels, being torn everywhere,</l>
<l>o our father, [and] covered with cicatrices, it is a bad mishap</l>
<l>for [your] feet like pretty lotuses.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
